          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "STTA",
                "GSPEC",
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Conventional stacked foil technique was used with",
                " bombarding deuteron beams of 1 to 20 MeV.",
                "Beam current was measured in Faraday cup.",
                "Energy degradation in the stack was determined by",
                " measuring equivalent aluminium thickness.",
                "Chemical separation was applied and with subsequent",
                " absolute beta+ counting using methane-flow",
                " proportional counter.",
                "Correction was made for energy spread and for recoil",
                " effect.",
                "Individual points are not presented since their",
                " identity was lost in the process of making",
                " corrections for the energy distribution of the",
                " deuteron beam.",
                "The process consisted of an inverse folding operation."
              ]
            }
          ],
